	care: `<svg viewBox="0 0 220 220" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect x="72" y="36" width="44" height="148" rx="20" fill="#FEF3DB"/><rect x="116" y="60" width="40" height="124" rx="20" fill="#E2F2FF"/><circle cx="94" cy="82" r="16" fill="#F7C2A4"/><circle cx="136" cy="94" r="14" fill="#8BCAE8"/></svg>`,
